tion.com/upload/general-english/58-who-what-where-and-why-2019-03-29-10-25-41/22.mp3","time_start":58.36,"time_end":60.9},{"position":23,"content":"They say that you should answer all of these questions if you are writing a good story.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/58-who-what-where-and-why-2019-03-29-10-25-41/23.mp3","time_start":61.68,"time_end":66.3},{"position":24,"content":"You have to give the who, what, where and why to write a good story.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/58-who-what-where-and-why-2019-03-29-10-25-41/24.mp3","time_start":66.4,"time_end":71.6}]}